<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạfḍl mn lmʿạn ạlsẖms nwr ạbrq ḥwly

[V2]
 ạnhy kl ḥyạẗ ạlạms wskn fy qlby

[V3]
 nwr ʿjyb nwr kyạny nwr wqwẗ hdmt ẓlạmy

[V4]
 ạlqrạr - hdạny lṭryq ạllẗ yswʿ ạlḥy ạbn ạllh

[V5]
